    "body": "Ran into temp dir cleanup errors on Windows, at first I tried to fix the wrong issue. Turned out it was a test bug creating and opening files without closing them.\r\n\r\nSo I introduced two new `testutil` functions `TempFile` (string) and `CreateTemp` (like `os.CreateTemp` with cleanup) and cleaned up the tests.",
